│ opt: llvm/include/llvm/IR/ValueHandle.h:95: llvm::Value& llvm::ValueHandleBase::operator*() const: Assertion `V && "Dereferencing deleted ValueHandle"' failed.                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
